{"tid":2400583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：市民要以客觀科學看待接種疫苗 勿有政治滲入","createTime":"2021-02-09T05:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T07:10:18.000Z","uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"0265252661d083291da8ec7d9dd7bd1431d771cd","tid":2400583,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:23:55.000Z","msg":"林鄭：市民要以客觀科學看待接種疫苗 勿有政治滲入<br />\n<br />\n#港聞 行政長官林鄭月娥表示，如疫情無惡化，年廿九至農曆新年假期期間不會封區強制檢測，而假期後亦會安排逐步復課復業。另外，科興疫苗數據將由顧問專家委員會審視，林鄭月娥指刊登醫學期刊只是其中一項要求，強調政府並沒有偏頗。 (2/9/13:16) 全文 (<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=423517\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D423517&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=4f0c1360\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D423517&h=1c57a6d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=423517</a>)"},{"pid":"9252f0bda41252b6e816042a722e7ffa6083b14f","tid":2400583,"uid":155095,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:25:29.000Z","msg":"客觀數據 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2021/01/14/f998ae2b3fa2a52161147c591e3ad31d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rti.org.tw%2Fassets%2Fthumbnails%2F2021%2F01%2F14%2Ff998ae2b3fa2a52161147c591e3ad31d.png&h=f880bd4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2b7d8f2f037a963505e764d72bc7ea306a384d2","tid":2400583,"uid":343712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:26:00.000Z","msg":"所以咪唔打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7839666895af67c2aaa08e19f84a23098361472a","tid":2400583,"uid":11291,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:26:24.000Z","msg":"我唔妥啲支那疫苗都係好客觀嘅事實"},{"pid":"5a1a7ccd6ab0ff6fb997c74f078fc84cdd2f52aa","tid":2400583,"uid":23635,"like":3,"dislike":